---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Nairobi's Trusted Car Key Heroes</h1>
			<p>
				You can be driving on any road in Nairobi and its environs, then you accidentally lose your keys, your car door locks you out, or your ignition grinds to a halt.  
			</p>
			<p>
				But what if there's a guide ready to transform your crisis into triumph?
			</p>
			<p>At Nairobi Car Key Replacement Locks, we are your automotive ally in Nairobi.	
			</p>
			<p>We're experienced locksmiths with over a decade of expertise helping car owners solve several car key issues.</p>
			<p>Here are the services we offer: </p>	
			<ul>
				<li>Car Key Replacements: Lost your keys? We craft precise replacements for all makes and models, from Toyota to Mercedes, using advanced laser-cutting technology.
				<li>Car Key Duplication and Spare Keys: Prevent future quests by duplicating your keys on-site. We make spares that match originals.</li> 
